#L_D2_ans20=You know, SAM, I'm only going to say this one time, so try to remember it. I attacked my friends only because I believed in your plan. I believe that we can both put an end to this bloodshed and avoid it in the future. I believe that you have everything calculated, sorted and classified. But if there are any raw spots in your plan, you must tell me about them before they turn into serious problems. Don't try to hide anything or I'll smash you to smithereens and neither Berserks or anything else will stop me!
#L_D2_msg30=I explain your aggressive behavior by psychological discomfort you are experiencing in the light of the recent events. As for hiding information, you will have full access to all databases after you have been connected to my network.
#L_D2_ans30=Hey, I haven't agreed to any "connections"! I won't let you plug pieces of metal into my brain!
#L_D2_msg40=I'd try it I guess. We'll have to do that anyway... I mean, to build a new world.
