#L_D2_msg50=I am afraid I must insist on implanting neurochips into your nervous system. Do not worry, this procedure is completely painless and safe. The neurochip can be removed in the future, when implanting has become voluntary. But not now when you have an important and dangerous mission ahead of you. Without implants your chances will only be 3.82% and I cannot take the risk.
